<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge">
    <meta content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" name="viewport">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
    <title>我的优惠券</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/tic-content.css">
</head>

<body>

    <section class="tab-panel">
      <div class="box">
        <div class="c-item">
          <img src="img/coupon/xichequan.png" alt="">
          <div class="c-info">
              <div class="c-top">
                  <div class="c-name">免费洗车券</div>
                  <div class="c-note">持有本优惠券可免费享受一次洗车服务</div>
              </div>
              <div class="c-date">有效日期：2017-02-02 --- 2017-10-02</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="tab-panel">
      <div class="rule">
        <div class="phase1">
          <h2>可用门店：</h2>
          <p>地址：北京市朝阳区酒仙桥驼房营路新华科技大厦0101</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>使用规则：</h2>
          <p>1. 一张优惠券仅可使用一次，且请在有效期内使用该券，否则逾期作废不可用。</p>
          <p>2. 用户可在优惠券上注明地址的门店里使用。</p>
          <p>3. 点击下方的“赠送他人”可将自己的优惠券赠他人使用。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel1">
      <h4>优惠券来源：</h4>
      <div class="box1a">
        <img src="./img/girl.png" alt="无法显示">
        <div class="box2a">
          <div class="box3a">
            <span class="title-name">某某某某</span>
            <span class="word2">2017-03-23 10:00</span>
          </div>
          <p class="word2 color-orange">送了你一张免费洗车券~</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="box5 box-record">
      <div class="box5-inner">
        <p>优惠券使用记录</p>
        <img src="./img/me/right.png" alt="无法显示">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="box5 lastChild">
      <div class="box5-inner">
        <p>优惠券赠送记录</p>
        <img src="./img/me/right.png" alt="无法显示">
      </div>
    </section>


    <section class="box3 btn">
      <div class="box2 box4">
        <span>赠送他人</span>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    document.getElementsByClassName('btn')[0].addEventListener('click',function(){
      window.location.href="./donateCard.html";
    })

    // 优惠券使用记录：
    document.getElementsByClassName('box-record')[0].addEventListener('click',function(){
      window.location.href="./use_record.html";
    })

    // 优惠券赠送记录：
    document.getElementsByClassName('lastChild')[0].addEventListener('click',function(){
      window.location.href="./donate_record.html";
    })

  </script>
</html>
